name: hiddenInputContainer & crossOrigin
body: Add hiddenInputContainer config and crossOrigin argument for images

name: v3.9.0
body:
- You can now specify `null` as thumbnail width or height and it will scale accordingly
- You can set a function as `paramName` option and it will be executed with `n`.

name: Bugfix for image generation of subsequent files
body: - [33624db](https://github.com/enyo/dropzone/commit/33624db3017cdbd792292e005e0fc25690b67d52) Fixed the bug that all subsequent file uploads don't generate a thumbnail.

name: "queuecomplete" event, thumbnail queue, data-dz-remove elements and fixed ios 'squash bug'
body:
You should not use this version, but version [v3.8.1](https://github.com/enyo/dropzone/releases/edit/v3.8.0) which fixes a queuecomplete bug.
- [d7c1640](https://github.com/enyo/dropzone/commit/d7c164091545cb95c3e50439ac42799698faab59) Fixed #17 the iOS 'image squash' bug.
- [014fea1](https://github.com/enyo/dropzone/commit/014fea1ec7d2c325498d2baca4ea1a2e954066b2) All elements with the data-dz-remove attribute are remove links now.
- [0b115f0](https://github.com/enyo/dropzone/commit/0b115f07a541e2da09f0c4442b57f4ad2e4e3379) The creation of thumbnails is now queued which strongly improves performance.
- [e41b595](https://github.com/enyo/dropzone/commit/e41b595c41a7c86453d2bdfda0eda579c789d096) Added the queuecomplete event that gets triggered when all files finished uploading.

name: Many bugfixes
body:
- [8c7b145](https://github.com/enyo/dropzone/commit/8c7b145b5f53631d2eb133ed52e3a92c4f7415ee) Fixed a problem with the image creation in latest Chrome versions.
- [f8705bb](https://github.com/enyo/dropzone/commit/f8705bb34d60926f310a13b7a0bb17ee829f85b1) Dropzone.optionsForElement doesn't throw now when called with a form that has an input with the name 'id'
- [6286a57](https://github.com/enyo/dropzone/commit/6286a5784cf5f57fed9fbe6c0ea59af207369efc) On error, if a JSON object is returned, the 'error' attribute is now used as error message if available.
- [a9e52d7](https://github.com/enyo/dropzone/commit/a9e52d7f893f1fab6e14b78502cef6e6ac8fee3d) Select inputs with the multiple keyword work properly now.
- [797bae6](https://github.com/enyo/dropzone/commit/797bae680ed15ef32a15acf428553b358176a975) Dropzone.destroy() removes itself from Dropzone.instances now.
- [8802f46](https://github.com/enyo/dropzone/commit/8802f4626ae9dc5985ebf262a002293fc72d3f09) Settings maxFiles to 0 works now.
- [d7f6c41](https://github.com/enyo/dropzone/commit/d7f6c414b4e58980feb20230e0c048a61eec788d) Dropzone doesn't crash anymore if a form has an input field with name 'id'
- [ac6e8f8](https://github.com/enyo/dropzone/commit/ac6e8f8d8917bc41ec448a5fc66feaaf5c69299a) Displaying filesizes in Mebibyte, gibibyte, etc... now.

name: Fix for download files
body: The previous release had an error and the download files didn't work.
This release also includes updated developer tools (Grunt)

name: `options.maxFiles` introduced!
body:
- [cfb43af](https://github.com/enyo/dropzone/commit/cfb43af761891ad8dd5dd80e9dcf5cd38cc6cd9b) Added a Dropzone.confirm function.
- [563340e](https://github.com/enyo/dropzone/commit/563340eef4aba2e71851bf425b536db40fe66cd9) Added a maxFiles option which provides the functionality to limit the Dropzone to a maximum nu
  mber of handled files.
- [26e1300](https://github.com/enyo/dropzone/commit/26e130059afb1f49b125f4342f295c6d9f7e001b) The dropzone element gets a dz-max-files-reached class now when maxFiles has been reached or e
  xceeded.

name: v3.6.2
body:
- [52b50d2](https://github.com/enyo/dropzone/commit/52b50d22a15437dc6fdf9a724d2689274005f8a1) Calling Dropzone.discover() tries to discover elements now even if Dropzone.autoDiscover is false.
- [62fbe18](https://github.com/enyo/dropzone/commit/62fbe18cead195a11446ede7aff46405a6dc7f17) The hidden input field always has the multiple attribute regardless of the uploadMultiple property.
- [78ab99a](https://github.com/enyo/dropzone/commit/78ab99a222ef205e3410621eac3a988ce63e3891) Added a dictRemoveFileConfirmation option that will force a confirmation dialog before removing a file.

name: Bugfix for getRejectedFiles() and additional tests.
body: This is a recommended upgrade for all `v3.6.0` users.

name: Introduced autoProcessQueue as well as uploadMultiple.
body:
- ([2bd1281](https://github.com/enyo/dropzone/commit/2bd12816947dd6c14300d0a5b799fc9a213413e3)) Removed the enqueueForUpload option and introduced the autoProcessQueue option instead.
- ([d4143dd](https://github.com/enyo/dropzone/commit/d4143ddb4fd4792fc561b466dc21f5ead060c937)) Unselected radio buttons aren't submitted anymore.
- Introduced the `uploadMultiple` option that allows to send multiple files in one request.

name: Prefixed all Dropzone classes with dz-
body:
- Increased `maxThumbnailFilesize` to 10
- Success and error responses are now parsed as JSON
- Minor bug fixes and improvements
- Tests added

name: First release without jQuery
body: This release removed all dependencies on jQuery.
